data.description: Completely updated northern New Mexico style town home in a fantastic downtown location.  Awe inspiring two level floor plan offers two fantastic living areas, large and private bedrooms, a stylish formal dining area, and a just remodeled eat-in kitchen with stainless appliances and granite counter tops. Nichos, vigas, wooden shutters, and soaring wood ceilings.  Huge loft area includes a wet bar.  Main floor master suite includes a custom, large garden tub, separate shower, and double vanity.  Outside enjoy a beautiful, relaxing balcony space and a private courtyard.  Walk to Old Town, great restaurants, and museums, with very easy access to I-40 and downtown.  Fresh paint, new stucco, refrigerated air.  This gorgeous corner lot town home has it all.  Be the first to enjoy its updates and many luxuries.
